    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <h3>What do I require for this application?</h3>
    <p>
    The application will work with an Android smart phone or an augmented reality glasses,
    it is recommended to use an augmented reality glasses for the best experience.
    </p>
    <h3>Is the application and registration free?</h3>
    <p>
    Yes, everything is free to use.
    </p>
    <h3>How do I use this application?</h3>
    <p>
    First create an account, and install the application on your device. Start the application
    and write down the given code. Login to your account and go into the Device Manager.
    In the text box, enter the code you retrieved from the application.
    </p>
    <h3>Why can't I add more than one device to my account?</h3>
    <p>
    For the simple reason that there can't be one person at two different places.
    </p>
    <h3>Can I change my device?</h3>
    <p>
    To change devices, you can remove the device at the Device Manager and add a new device.
    </p>
